title: Jira: Custom Service
agents: jira
catalog: app/jira
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 With this check you can monitor custom Jira queries. It outputs the number of
 search results in the defined way (count, sum, average) of the related
 datasource.

 Needs the datasource "Check statistics of Jira" to be configured.

item:
 The item is the name of custom service defined in the datasource rule.

discovery:
 One service is created for each custom service configured within the datasource rule.
 E.g. {"Jira My_custom_service_name"}.
